    <entry>
      <title>读书笔记：代码整洁之道</title>
      <link href="/2026/06/15/reading-notes/"/>
      <url>/2026/06/15/reading-notes/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>最近重读了《代码整洁之道》，整理了一些重要的观点。</p><h2 id="核心观点"><a href="#核心观点" class="headerlink" title="核心观点"></a>核心观点</h2><blockquote><p>“写整洁代码，需要遵循大量的小技巧，贯彻刻苦习得的’整洁感’。” —— Robert C. Martin</p></blockquote><h2 id="关于命名"><a href="#关于命名" class="headerlink" title="关于命名"></a>关于命名</h2><p><strong>好的命名应该：</strong></p><ul><li>名副其实</li><li>避免误导</li><li>做有意义的区分</li><li>可读、可搜索</li></ul><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 不好的命名</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> d = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Date</span>();</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> temp = <span class="title function_">calculateTemperature</span>();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 好的命名</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> currentDate = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Date</span>();</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> celsiusTemperature = <span class="title function_">calculateTemperature</span>();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="关于函数"><a href="#关于函数" class="headerlink" title="关于函数"></a>关于函数</h2><p><strong>函数应该：</strong></p><ul><li>短小</li><li>只做一件事</li><li>每个函数一个抽象层次</li></ul><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 不好的写法</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">processUserData</span>(<span class="params">user</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 验证用户</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> (!user.<span class="property">name</span> || !user.<span class="property">email</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">throw</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Error</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;Invalid user&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 格式化数据</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">const</span> formatted = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">name</span>: user.<span class="property">name</span>.<span class="title function_">trim</span>(),</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">email</span>: user.<span class="property">email</span>.<span class="title function_">toLowerCase</span>()</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 保存到数据库</span></span><br><span class="line">  database.<span class="title function_">save</span>(formatted);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 好的写法</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">validateUser</span>(<span class="params">user</span>) &#123; ... &#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">formatUserData</span>(<span class="params">user</span>) &#123; ... &#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">saveUser</span>(<span class="params">user</span>) &#123; ... &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">processUserData</span>(<span class="params">user</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="title function_">validateUser</span>(user);</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">const</span> formatted = <span class="title function_">formatUserData</span>(user);</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="title function_">saveUser</span>(formatted);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="关于注释"><a href="#关于注释" class="headerlink" title="关于注释"></a>关于注释</h2><p><strong>注释的坏味道：</strong></p><ul><li>多余的注释</li><li>误导性注释</li><li>日志式注释</li><li>注释掉的代码</li></ul><blockquote><p>“别给糟糕的代码加注释——重写它。”</p></blockquote><h2 id="关于格式"><a href="#关于格式" class="headerlink" title="关于格式"></a>关于格式</h2><p><strong>代码格式很重要：</strong></p><ul><li>垂直格式：相关代码靠近</li><li>水平格式：适当缩进，避免过长行</li><li>团队统一风格</li></ul><hr><p>这本书值得每个程序员反复阅读。</p>]]></content>
      
      
